data-triple-N3.o: "West Bromwich Albion Football Club, also known as West Brom, The Baggies, The Throstles, Albion or WBA, are an English professional football club based in West Bromwich in the West Midlands. The club was formed in 1878 and have played at their home ground since 1900. Albion were one of the founding members of The Football League in 1888 and have spent the majority of their existence in the top tier of English football."@en
